## Semantic tokens (what components reference)

| Token | Purpose | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| `--color-text-primary` | Default text | Must meet WCAG AA against background |
| `--color-text-muted` | De-emphasized text | Still ≥ 4.5:1 |
| `--color-bg` | Default background | — |
| `--color-surface` | Elevated surfaces | Cards, panels |
| `--color-border` | Default hairline | — |
| `--color-primary` | Brand / primary action | — |
| {{...}} | {{...}} | {{...}} |

